[SHORT DESC]
Enemies' contact moves have a 30% chance to burn them. Halves the amount of steps required to hatch Eggs.
[LONG DESC]
<p>When an enemy uses a contact move against this Pok√©mon, there is a 30% chance of burning the enemy. If the attack does no damage, Flame Body does not activate.</p>

<p>Based on the initial number of steps required to hatch an Egg, Flame Body will reduce the number of steps required in the following manner:</p>

